<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reports – CA Prakash M Oswal & Co.</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f7f6f2;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --surface-alt: #f0eee8;
      --border: #ddd7cc;
      --text: #26231b;
      --text-muted: #77736a;
      --primary: #002855;
      --primary-dark: #003d7a;
      --accent: #ff7f32;
      --radius: 10px;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      background: rgba(247, 246, 242, 0.96);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.1rem;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .nav-link {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    }

    .nav-link::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      transition: width 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    .nav-link:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-reports-btn {
      padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 40, 85, 0.18);
      transition: background 0.2s ease-out, transform 0.1s ease-out,
        box-shadow 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    .nav-reports-btn:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 40, 85, 0.25);
    }

    main {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .hero {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 1.8rem auto 1.8rem;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .hero-heading {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 36rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }

    .hero-meta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .hero-tag {
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--surface-alt);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .section {
      padding: 0 1.5rem 2.2rem;
    }

    .section-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .reports-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.7fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
      gap: 1.8rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .report-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .report-title {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .report-meta {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .report-description {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: none;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 40, 85, 0.25);
      transition: background 0.2s ease-out, transform 0.1s ease-out,
        box-shadow 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(0, 40, 85, 0.32);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s ease-out, border-color 0.2s ease-out;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--surface-alt);
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .report-sidebar {
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .sidebar-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 0.9rem 0.9rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .sidebar-card h3 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem 1.2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 880px) {
      .reports-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 0.4rem;
      }
      .nav-links {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
      .hero {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <div class="nav">
        <div class="brand">
          <div class="brand-title">CA PRAKASH M OSWAL & CO.</div>
          <div class="brand-sub">Chartered Accountants · Pune</div>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="CA-Prakash-Oswal-Website-UPDATED (1) (1).html#services" class="nav-link">Services</a>
          <a href="CA-Prakash-Oswal-Website-UPDATED (1) (1).html#about" class="nav-link">About</a>
          <a href="CA-Prakash-Oswal-Website-UPDATED (1) (1).html#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
          <!-- Right-most: current page -->
          <a href="reports.html" class="nav-reports-btn">Reports</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div>
          <div class="hero-eyebrow">Reports & Thought Leadership</div>
          <h1 class="hero-heading">Internal Audit in Real Life – Practical Report</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
            A practitioner’s view on how internal audit actually works inside organisations –
            beyond textbook definitions – with a focus on process, risk, controls, and value
            addition.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-meta">
            <span class="hero-tag">Internal Audit</span>
            <span class="hero-tag">Practical Report</span>
            <span class="hero-tag">PDF</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-inner">
          <div class="reports-grid">
            <article class="report-card">
              <h2 class="report-title">
                Internal Audit in Real Life – Practical Report
              </h2>
              <p class="report-meta">
                Category: Internal Audit · Format: PDF
              </p>
              <p class="report-description">
                This report walks through the internal audit lifecycle as it plays out in real
                organisations – from understanding the business and risk landscape, to planning
                fieldwork, executing tests, interacting with process owners, and converting
                observations into practical, accepted recommendations.
              </p>
              <p class="report-description">
                It is designed for promoters, finance leaders, internal auditors, and students
                who want an implementable, ground-level view of internal audit – not just
                theoretical frameworks. The tone is conversational and example-driven, drawing
                from real assignments handled by the firm.
              </p>
              <!-- IMPORTANT: put the PDF file in the same folder with this exact name or update the href -->
              <a
                href="Internal-Audit-in-Real-Life-Final.pdf"
                class="btn-primary"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
              >
                View PDF report
              </a>
            </article>

            <aside class="report-sidebar">
              <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>How to use this report</h3>
                <p>
                  Share it with your internal teams, audit committee, or process owners to
                  align expectations on what a meaningful internal audit engagement should
                  deliver.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="sidebar-card">
                <h3>Future reports</h3>
                <p>
                  Additional reports on governance, risk management, controls, and taxation
                  can be added on this page as they are authored. Each new report can be
                  listed below with a similar card and download link.
                </p>
              </div>
            </aside>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div>© <span id="year"></span> CA Prakash M Oswal & Co. All rights reserved.</div>
        <div>Internal audit, risk, and controls – practical insights from real assignments</div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
